<emphasis id="A8AAEAE1F000FFB9FEA9F8281865F82F" box="[281,551,2007,2028]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="298">Bradysiopsis praevittigera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="A8AAEAE1F000FFB9FD9CF8281827F82F" bold="true" box="[556,613,2007,2028]" pageId="5" pageNumber="298">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="B399579AF000FFB9FD9CF8281827F82F" box="[556,613,2007,2028]" pageId="5" pageNumber="298" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
Holotype. 
<emphasis id="A8AAEAE1F000FFB9FD67F82918ABF828" bold="true" box="[727,745,2006,2027]" pageId="5" pageNumber="298">A</emphasis>
. Gonostylus, ventral view. 
<emphasis id="A8AAEAE1F000FFB9FC4EF8281E4DF82F" bold="true" box="[1022,1039,2007,2028]" pageId="5" pageNumber="298">B</emphasis>
. Flagellomeres 3–4. 
<emphasis id="A8AAEAE1F000FFB9FB54F8291EB4F82F" bold="true" box="[1252,1270,2006,2028]" pageId="5" pageNumber="298">C</emphasis>
. Wing.
</paragraph>
